# Files excluded from the graphify knowledge graph (gitignore syntax).
#
# Point-in-time records are append-only by convention: they are never rewritten
# when the design moves on, so indexing them freezes superseded designs and
# already-fixed findings into the graph and query answers go stale. Living
# documentation (README.md, CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, docs/DEPLOY.md) is kept.
docs/superpowers/
docs/*-review-*.md
docs/feature-suggestions-*.md

# Image material with no queryable structure.
docs/screenshots/

# Agent tooling, not project code: skill definitions, harness settings, and the
# subagent task briefs / reports / review diffs written during development.
# Graphify skips dot-directories by default; these are listed explicitly so the
# exclusion does not depend on that default.
.claude/
.agents/
.superpowers/
.codex/
